               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Wǝddāse ʾAmlāk “Praise of God” (fols. 2ra-123rb)&#xD;
I-1) Monday’s prayer of Basil of Caesarea (fols. 2ra-16ra)&#xD;
I-2) Tuesday’s prayer of Efrem the Syrian (fols. 16rb-39vb)&#xD;
I-3) Wednesday’s prayer of Efrem the Syrian (fols. 39vb-57ra)&#xD;
I-4) Thursday’s prayer of John Saba (ʾAragāwi Manfasawi) (fols. 57rb-78va)&#xD;
I-5) Friday’s prayer of Shenute (78va-88ra) and Pachomius (fols. 88ra-96rb)&#xD;
I-6) Saturday’s prayer of Athanasius of Alexandria (fols. 96rb-109rb)&#xD;
I-7) Sunday’s prayer of Cyril of Alexandria (fols. 109rb-123rb)&#xD;
II) ʾArgānona wǝddāse “The Harp of Praise” (fols. 124ra-233rb)&#xD;
II-1) Monday (fols. 124ra-143ra)&#xD;
II-2) Tuesday (fols. 144ra-161vb)&#xD;
II-3) Wednesday (fols. 162ra-179va)&#xD;
II-4) Thursday (fols. 180ra-198rb)&#xD;
II-5) Friday (fols. 198rb-214va)&#xD;
II-6) Saturday (fols. 214vb-223va)&#xD;
II-7) Sunday (fols. 223vb-233rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
